uff take a one week break and do other things Think about EQ and why you get mad at it when its not Real Life.  Because we all know if it was Real Life i would have killed you all and fed you to my pet LONG AGO.  I will see you all  in 12 days.<br>
Please keep me posted on anything that might have happened <br>
&lt;ex. who took Sonnya's leader tag when she left&gt;<br>
